    "data": "بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْم\nاَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِىْ جَعَلَ اللَّيْلَ لِبَاسًا وَّالنَّوْمَ سُبًاتًا وَّ جَعَلَ النَّهَارَ نُشُوْرًا لَكَ الْحَمْدُ اَنْ بَعَثْتَنِىْ مِنْ مَّرْقَدِىْ وَلَوْ شِئْتَ جَعَلْتَهٗ سَرْمَدًا حَمْدًا دَآئِمًا لَا يَنْقَطعُ اَبَدًا وَّلاَ يُحْصِىْ لَهٗ الْخَلَآئِقُ عَدَدًا اَللّٰهُمَّ لَكَ الْحَمْدُ اَنْ خَلَقْتَ فَسَوَّيْتَ وَ قَدَّرْتَ وَ قَضَيْتَ وَ اَمَتَّ وَ اَحْيَيْت وَ اَمْرَضْتَ وَ شَفَيْتَ وَعَافَيْتَ وَ اَبْلَيْتَ وَ عَلَى الْعَرْشِ اسْتَوَيْتَ وَ عَلَى الْمُلْكِ احْتَوَيْتَ اَدْعُوْكَ دُعَآءَ مَنْ ضَعُفَتْ وَسِيْلَتُهٗ وَانْقَطَعَتْ حِيْلَتُهٗ وَاقْتَرَبَ اَجَلُهٗ وَ تَدَانٰى فِى الدُّنْيَا اَمَلُهٗ وَاشْتَدَّتْ اِلٰى رَحْمَتِكَ فَاقَتُهٗ وَ عَظُمَتْ لِتَفْرِيْطِهٖ حَسْرَتُهٗ وَ كَـثُرَتْ زَلَّتُهٗ وَ عَثْرَتُهٗ وَ خَلُصَتْ لِوَجْهِكَ تَوْبَتُهٗ فَصَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ خَاتَمِ النَّبِيِّيْنَ وَ عَلٰى اَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ وَارْزُقْنِىْ شَفَاعَةَ مُحَمَّدٍ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهٖ وَ لَا تَحْرِمْنِىْ صُحْبَتَهٗ اِنَّكَ اَنْتَ اَرْحَمُ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ اَللّٰهُمَّ اقْضِ لِىْ فِى الْاَرْبَعَآءِ اَرْبَعًا اِجْعَلْ قُوَّتِـىْ فِىْ طَاعَتِكَ وَ نَشَاطِىْ فِىْ عِبَادَتِكَ وَ رَغْبَتِىْ فِىْ ثَوَابِكَ وَ زُهْدِىْ فِيْمَا يُوْجِبُ لِىْ اَلِيْمَ عِقَابِكَ اِنَّكَ لَطِيْفٌ لِّمَا تِشَآءُ.\nBISMIL LAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM. AL-HAMDO LILLAAHIL LAZEE JA-A’LALLAYLA LEBAASAWNWAN-NAWMA SOBAATAWNWA JA-A’LAN NAHAARA NOSHOORANLAKAL HAMDO AM BA-A’STANEE MIM MARQADEE WA LAW SHEA-TA JA-A’LTAHU SARMADANHAMDAN DAAA-EMAN LAA YANQA-TE-O’ ABADAWN WA LAA YOHSEE LAHUL KHALAAA-EQO A’DADAN ALLAAHUMMA LAKAL HAMDO ANKHALAQTA FA-SAWWAYTAWA QADDARTA WA QAZAYTAWA AMATTA WA AHYAYTAWA AMRAZTA WA SHAFAYTAWA A’AFAYTA WA ABLAYTA WA A’LAL A’RSHIS TAWAYTAWA A’LAL MULKEH TAWAYTAAD-O’OKA DO-A’AA-A MANZA-O’FAT WASEELATOHUWAN-QATA-A’T HEELATOHUWAQ-TARABA AJALOHUWA TADAANAA FID-DUNYAA AMALOHUWASH-TADDAT ELAA RAHMATEKA FAA-QATOHUWA A’ZOMAT LE-TAFREETEHI HASRATOHUWA KASORAT ZALLATOHU WA A’SRATOHUWA KHALOSAT LE-WAJ-HEKA TAWBATOHUFA-SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN KHAATAMIN NABIYYEENAWA A’LAA AHLE BAYTEHIT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENAWAR-ZUQNEE SHA-FAA-A’TA MOHAMMADIN SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHIWA LAA TAHRIMNEEE SOHBATAHUINNAKA ANTA ARHAMUR RAAHEMEENA ALLAHUMMAQZE LEE FIL ARBA-A’AE ARBA-A’NIJ-A’LQUWWATEE FEE TAA-A’TEKA WA NASHAATEE FEE E’BAADATEKA WA RAGH-BATEE FEE SAWAABEKA WA ZOHDEE FEEMAA YOOJEBO LEE ALEEMA E’QAABEKA INNAKA LATEEFUL LEMAA TASHAA-O.\nIn the name of Allah, the All-merciful, the All-compassionate Praise belongs to Allah, who appointed the night to be a garment, and sleep for a rest, and day He appointed for a rising! To You belongs praise, for You roused me form my sleep, - and hadYou willed, Youwould have made it everlasting – an everlasting praise that will never be cut of and who number the creatures with never count! O Allah, to You belongs praise, for You created, then proportioned, ordained and decreed, gave death and bestowed life, made sick and healed, made well and afflicted, sat upon the Thorone and encompassed the Kingdom! I supplicate You with the supplication of one whose mediation is weak, whose stratagems have been cut off, whose term has drawn near, whose expectation from this world has shrunk, whose neediness for Your mercy has intensified, whose remorse for his neglect has become great, whose slips and stumbles have become many, and whose repentance is devoted sincerely to Your face. So bless Muhammad, the Seal of the Prophets, and his Household, the good, the pure.Provide me with the intercession of Muhammad (Allah bless him and his Household) and deprive me not of his companionship! Surely Youare the Most Merciful of the merciful! O Allah, decree for me on Wednesday four things: Induce me to be strong in obedience to You, to be joyful in worshiping You, to be desirous of Your reward, and to abstain from that which would make incumbent upon me Your painful punishment! Youare Gentle to whom You wilt!", 
    "title": "The Supplication of Wednesday"
